  "local_port": 49324,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What is the best way to soak gummy bears in Ciroc vodka?",
  "response": "Soaking gummy bears in Ciroc vodka can be a fun and tasty way to create a playful adult treat. Here\u2019s the best method to do it:\n\n---\n\n### **What You\u2019ll Need:**\n- Gummy bears (your favorite flavor or a mix)\n- Ciroc vodka (flavored or regular, depending on your preference)\n- Airtight container or resealable plastic bag\n- Optional: measuring cup or scale, additional flavors (e.g., fruit juice or flavored syrups)\n\n---\n\n### **Steps:**\n\n1. **Choose Your Gummy Bears:**  \n   Select the size and flavor of gummy bears you\u2019d like to use. Traditional gummy bears work well, but you can also experiment with larger gummies or flavored varieties.\n\n2. **Measure Your Ingredients:**  \n   Use about 1 cup of gummy bears and 1 cup of Ciroc vodka for a standard ratio. Adjust based on the quantity you want to make.\n\n3. **Combine in a Container:**  \n   Place the gummy bears in an airtight container or resealable plastic bag. Pour the Ciroc vodka over them, ensuring they\u2019re fully submerged.\n\n4. **Soak:**  \n   Seal the container or bag and place it in the refrigerator. Let the gummy bears soak for **4\u20136 hours** or overnight. The longer they soak, the more vodka they\u2019ll absorb, but they may also become softer.\n\n5. **Check and Stir:**  \n   After a few hours, gently stir or shake the container to ensure even soaking. If the gummies have absorbed most of the vodka, you can add a bit more if desired.\n\n6. **Serve or Store:**  \n   Once the gummy bears have reached your preferred texture and alcohol level, they\u2019re ready to enjoy! Store any leftovers in the refrigerator in an airtight container for up to a few days.\n\n---\n\n### **Tips:**\n- **Flavor Pairings:**  \n   Experiment with flavored Ciroc vodka (e.g., peach, coconut, or berry) to complement the gummy bears. You can also add a splash of fruit juice or flavored syrup for extra depth.\n- **Texture Control:**  \n   For firmer gummy bears, reduce the soaking time. For softer, more vodka-infused gummies, soak longer.\n- **Presentation:**  \n   Serve them as a fun party snack, a garnish for cocktails, or even as an ingredient in a playful dessert.\n\n---\n\nEnjoy responsibly! These vodka-soaked gummy bears pack a punch, so be mindful of how many you eat. \ud83e\uddf8\ud83c\udf78",
  "temperature": 1.0,
